00:00:31.721 --> 00:00:34.226 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ Gives me strength

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:37.899 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ And courage to know

00:00:37.932 --> 00:00:42.006 position:13% line:5% align:start
♪ I will make it through

