♪ Summer's sweet scent

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:02.975 position:21% line:5% align:start
♪ Autumn's whisper

00:01:03.008 --> 00:01:06.982 position:5% line:5% align:start
♪ Winter stings with the cold

00:01:07.015 --> 00:01:12.258 position:21% line:5% align:start
♪ When trouble comes
rolling in like thunder ♪

00:01:13.894 --> 00:01:17.767 position:24% line:89% align:start
♪ Tears may fall

00:01:17.801 --> 00:01:21.139 position:27% line:89% align:start
♪ Fear may call

00:01:21.174 --> 00:01:26.015 position:7% line:89% align:start
♪ But with spring in my heart

00:01:26.048 --> 00:01:28.152 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ When seasons change

00:01:28.186 --> 00:01:29.555 position:16% line:89% align:start
♪ I'll change with them

00:01:29.588 --> 00:01:35.999 position:24% line:83% align:start
♪ And I know I can
weather the storm ♪

00:01:37.334 --> 00:01:40.339 position:10% line:89% align:start
- Birk, what's gonna happen?

00:01:41.609 --> 00:01:43.579 position:16% line:83% align:start
- [Narrator] As the clash
between Mattis and Borka

00:01:43.612 --> 00:01:46.284 position:5% line:89% align:start
grew more intense, Ronja worried

00:01:46.317 --> 00:01:48.453 position:10% line:89% align:start
about what might happen next.

00:01:49.856 --> 00:01:52.427 position:27% line:83% align:start
Then she returned
home from the forest

00:01:52.460 --> 00:01:57.303 position:13% line:83% align:start
to the awful sight of Birk,
who was captured by Mattis.

00:01:57.336 --> 00:01:59.105 position:19% line:89% align:start
I hate you, she cried.

00:02:00.274 --> 00:02:03.146 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ronja had always loved
her father dearly,

00:02:03.179 --> 00:02:05.517 position:7% line:89% align:start
but now she only despised him.

00:02:05.550 --> 00:02:07.887 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:02:09.356 --> 00:02:11.493 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mattis!

00:02:32.196 --> 00:02:33.431 position:27% line:89% align:start
- Here they come.

00:02:33.465 --> 00:02:35.534 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:02:38.206 --> 00:02:40.209 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:02:45.719 --> 00:02:46.620 position:35% line:89% align:start
(cries out)

00:02:46.653 --> 00:02:48.223 position:38% line:89% align:start
- My boy!

00:03:23.717 --> 00:03:25.987 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:03:27.089 --> 00:03:29.694 position:24% line:89% align:start
(door creaks open)

00:03:29.727 --> 00:03:32.232 position:24% line:89% align:start
(door creaks shut)

00:03:32.265 --> 00:03:35.003 position:30% line:89% align:start
(floor creaks)

00:03:35.037 --> 00:03:37.308 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:03:42.249 --> 00:03:44.320 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:03:55.706 --> 00:03:58.244 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:04:01.616 --> 00:04:03.720 position:30% line:89% align:start
(ominous music)

00:04:03.753 --> 00:04:05.756 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:04:25.658 --> 00:04:26.525 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Birk!

00:04:26.559 --> 00:04:28.395 position:19% line:89% align:start
Birk, are you alright?!

00:04:32.235 --> 00:04:35.641 position:21% line:83% align:start
Mattis, you good for
nothing dirty beast!

00:04:36.843 --> 00:04:40.249 position:27% line:83% align:start
Bring my son back
here this instant

00:04:40.282 --> 00:04:45.157 position:13% line:83% align:start
or I'll tear off your legs
and rip out your eyes!

00:04:45.190 --> 00:04:47.394 position:7% line:89% align:start
Do you hear me, you scoundrel?!

00:04:47.428 --> 00:04:50.299 position:24% line:83% align:start
Do you have nothing
to say for yourself?

00:04:50.333 --> 00:04:53.539 position:21% line:83% align:start
Or is it that you're
so ashamed of yourself,

00:04:53.572 --> 00:04:55.809 position:21% line:89% align:start
you can't even speak?

00:04:55.843 --> 00:04:56.644 position:41% line:89% align:start
Well?!

00:04:56.677 --> 00:04:59.247 position:19% line:89% align:start
Say something, Mattis!

00:04:59.281 --> 00:05:01.653 position:7% line:89% align:start
- Tell her to be quiet, Borka.

00:05:02.888 --> 00:05:05.192 position:19% line:83% align:start
It would be better for
everyone if you listened

00:05:05.225 --> 00:05:08.865 position:16% line:83% align:start
to what I have to say and
keep your woman out of this.

00:05:08.898 --> 00:05:13.271 position:24% line:83% align:start
- Why are you just
standing there, Borka?

00:05:13.306 --> 00:05:15.744 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why don't you say something?!

00:05:17.981 --> 00:05:21.487 position:27% line:83% align:start
- You must have a
heart of stone, Mattis.

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:22.856 position:33% line:89% align:start
- Hey, stop!

00:05:22.889 --> 00:05:24.960 position:19% line:89% align:start
Get your hands off me!

00:05:24.993 --> 00:05:27.463 position:21% line:89% align:start
- You're a vile man.

00:05:27.497 --> 00:05:29.601 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can understand that
you want me out of here,

00:05:29.634 --> 00:05:34.676 position:19% line:83% align:start
but you must understand
that's my son,

00:05:34.709 --> 00:05:38.482 position:21% line:83% align:start
my child who you used
to get what you want.

00:05:38.516 --> 00:05:40.720 position:13% line:89% align:start
Have you no sense of shame?

00:05:41.955 --> 00:05:45.294 position:24% line:83% align:start
- I didn't ask what
you think of me.

00:05:45.327 --> 00:05:47.230 position:7% line:89% align:start
What I want to know is how soon

00:05:47.264 --> 00:05:50.003 position:27% line:83% align:start
you'll be getting
out of my fort.

00:05:50.036 --> 00:05:52.273 position:38% line:89% align:start
(growls)

00:05:52.306 --> 00:05:54.209 position:38% line:89% align:start
(seethes)

00:06:04.293 --> 00:06:06.597 position:19% line:83% align:start
- First I have to find
a place in the forest

00:06:06.630 --> 00:06:09.803 position:5% line:89% align:start
where we can stay out of danger,

00:06:09.837 --> 00:06:12.942 position:24% line:83% align:start
but that may prove
difficult for us.

00:06:12.975 --> 00:06:16.347 position:19% line:83% align:start
That said, give me back
my son and I promise

00:06:16.380 --> 00:06:20.889 position:21% line:83% align:start
that we will be gone
before the summer is over.

00:06:20.922 --> 00:06:22.257 position:27% line:89% align:start
You have my word.

00:06:23.459 --> 00:06:24.628 position:30% line:89% align:start
- Sounds good.

00:06:26.065 --> 00:06:29.704 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then I in turn promise that
you will get your son back

00:06:29.737 --> 00:06:31.841 position:13% line:89% align:start
before the summer is over.

00:06:33.577 --> 00:06:38.519 position:24% line:83% align:start
- I meant, Mattis,
that I want my son back

00:06:38.552 --> 00:06:39.454 position:35% line:89% align:start
right now.

00:06:40.556 --> 00:06:44.096 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Well then you
better go right now.

00:06:44.129 --> 00:06:45.531 position:38% line:89% align:start
(growls)

00:06:45.564 --> 00:06:47.333 position:33% line:89% align:start
- You animal!

00:06:47.367 --> 00:06:50.740 position:24% line:83% align:start
I hope the harpies
rip ya to pieces!

00:06:50.773 --> 00:06:52.476 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:06:53.979 --> 00:06:59.856 position:10% line:83% align:start
- Bet ya know, Borka, we have
dungeons here in Mattis' fort.

00:06:59.889 --> 00:07:02.794 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your son won't want for
a roof over his head

00:07:02.828 --> 00:07:05.032 position:21% line:89% align:start
or food on his plate,

00:07:05.065 --> 00:07:08.436 position:7% line:89% align:start
so let that be a comfort to you

00:07:08.470 --> 00:07:11.642 position:24% line:83% align:start
if it happens to be
a cold, wet summer.

00:07:14.047 --> 00:07:16.550 position:33% line:89% align:start
(water drips)

00:07:29.807 --> 00:07:32.044 position:35% line:89% align:start
(sniffles)

00:07:34.115 --> 00:07:37.654 position:30% line:83% align:start
- I should just
destroy everything

00:07:37.687 --> 00:07:41.493 position:27% line:83% align:start
then Mattis will
know how I suffer.

00:07:41.526 --> 00:07:44.032 position:33% line:89% align:start
(water drips)

00:07:52.213 --> 00:07:54.583 position:38% line:89% align:start
(dinging)

00:08:02.664 --> 00:08:04.935 position:35% line:89% align:start
(whistling)

00:08:13.616 --> 00:08:15.919 position:16% line:89% align:start
- What's wrong with you?

00:08:15.954 --> 00:08:18.157 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't you feel well?

00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:20.127 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:08:21.930 --> 00:08:24.000 position:38% line:89% align:start
(laughs)

00:08:27.306 --> 00:08:29.911 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't you want to play?

00:08:29.944 --> 00:08:31.714 position:19% line:89% align:start
Here, watch once more.

00:08:33.850 --> 00:08:35.619 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:08:35.653 --> 00:08:37.290 position:35% line:89% align:start
Beat that!

00:08:37.323 --> 00:08:38.158 position:35% line:89% align:start
If you can.

00:08:45.838 --> 00:08:48.275 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:08:48.309 --> 00:08:51.180 position:27% line:89% align:start
(dramatic music)

00:08:53.351 --> 00:08:55.554 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:08:57.190 --> 00:08:59.261 position:38% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:09:04.904 --> 00:09:07.175 position:35% line:89% align:start
(wooshing)

00:09:17.959 --> 00:09:20.230 position:35% line:89% align:start
(rumbling)

00:09:34.321 --> 00:09:36.292 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasping)

00:09:53.821 --> 00:09:55.824 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:09:57.228 --> 00:09:58.363 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:09:58.396 --> 00:10:00.666 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:10:00.700 --> 00:10:04.907 position:21% line:83% align:start
- You're not the only
people who have dungeons.

00:10:04.940 --> 00:10:08.179 position:16% line:83% align:start
So your daughter will not
want for a roof over her head

00:10:08.213 --> 00:10:10.950 position:10% line:89% align:start
or food on her plate either.

00:10:10.984 --> 00:10:14.690 position:21% line:83% align:start
Comfort yourself with
that thought, Mattis.

00:10:19.466 --> 00:10:23.105 position:19% line:83% align:start
- Yes, cry, I would do
the same if I had a beast

00:10:23.138 --> 00:10:25.376 position:7% line:89% align:start
like that Mattis as my father.

00:10:26.411 --> 00:10:28.948 position:10% line:89% align:start
- I'm warning you, be quiet.

00:10:30.451 --> 00:10:32.888 position:7% line:89% align:start
You will not interfere in this.

00:10:32.922 --> 00:10:33.722 position:38% line:89% align:start
(scoffs)

00:10:33.756 --> 00:10:34.824 position:30% line:89% align:start
- How dare you!

00:10:34.858 --> 00:10:37.397 position:30% line:89% align:start
(woman grunts)

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:45.977 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:10:57.497 --> 00:10:59.968 position:10% line:89% align:start
- Do you hear that, ya fool?

00:11:00.002 --> 00:11:03.074 position:24% line:83% align:start
If you want to see
your daughter again,

00:11:03.107 --> 00:11:05.411 position:10% line:89% align:start
you will return my son to me!

00:11:11.955 --> 00:11:15.795 position:19% line:83% align:start
Mattis, will you bring
my son back over here

00:11:15.829 --> 00:11:19.402 position:24% line:83% align:start
or do I throw your
daughter into our dungeon?

00:11:19.435 --> 00:11:25.312 position:19% line:83% align:start
- You can have your son
back whenever you want.

00:11:25.345 --> 00:11:27.248 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Whenever I want?

00:11:27.282 --> 00:11:29.819 position:24% line:83% align:start
Shall we wait 'til
summer is over?

00:11:29.853 --> 00:11:30.955 position:30% line:89% align:start
You want that?

00:11:34.461 --> 00:11:36.131 position:21% line:89% align:start
- Whenever you want.

00:11:38.602 --> 00:11:43.209 position:19% line:83% align:start
- Look, I am merciful,
not a scoundrel,

00:11:43.243 --> 00:11:45.981 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll do a fair
exchange with you.

00:11:47.283 --> 00:11:49.887 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you give me back my
son, you will get back

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:53.026 position:24% line:83% align:start
your own child, you
heartless villain.

00:11:56.231 --> 00:11:58.869 position:24% line:89% align:start
- I have no child.

00:11:59.538 --> 00:12:01.307 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:12:01.341 --> 00:12:03.445 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasping)

00:12:04.613 --> 00:12:07.984 position:24% line:89% align:start
I have no daughter.

00:12:11.625 --> 00:12:14.229 position:7% line:89% align:start
- What's that supposed to mean?

00:12:14.262 --> 00:12:18.604 position:10% line:83% align:start
Is this some sort of mischief
you're trying to brew up?

00:12:18.637 --> 00:12:19.605 position:41% line:89% align:start
Is it?!

00:12:25.248 --> 00:12:28.554 position:24% line:83% align:start
- Feel free to take
your son, Borka,

00:12:28.588 --> 00:12:33.462 position:30% line:83% align:start
however I can't
take back my child.

00:12:35.065 --> 00:12:37.636 position:16% line:89% align:start
For I no longer have one.

00:12:38.571 --> 00:12:40.107 position:35% line:89% align:start
- But I do!

00:12:40.141 --> 00:12:42.645 position:16% line:89% align:start
I do and I want her back!

00:12:42.678 --> 00:12:43.479 position:35% line:89% align:start
(wooshing)

00:12:43.513 --> 00:12:46.652 position:33% line:89% align:start
(crow crows)

00:12:46.685 --> 00:12:50.559 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now you bring my child
back here, hear me?

00:12:50.592 --> 00:12:51.728 position:35% line:89% align:start
Right now.

00:12:51.761 --> 00:12:52.929 position:41% line:89% align:start
Borka!

00:12:54.365 --> 00:12:57.671 position:21% line:83% align:start
Even if that child's
father has gone crazy,

00:12:57.704 --> 00:12:59.474 position:19% line:89% align:start
as crazy as they come.

00:13:01.477 --> 00:13:03.614 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:13:17.738 --> 00:13:20.643 position:24% line:89% align:start
(soft piano music)

00:13:40.778 --> 00:13:43.315 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:13:46.822 --> 00:13:47.657 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:13:48.859 --> 00:13:51.463 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:13:51.496 --> 00:13:52.298 position:33% line:89% align:start
(sheep baa's)

00:13:52.331 --> 00:13:55.671 position:24% line:89% align:start
(door creaks open)

00:13:55.704 --> 00:13:57.841 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:13:57.874 --> 00:14:00.646 position:24% line:89% align:start
(door creaks shut)

00:14:00.679 --> 00:14:02.750 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:14:06.355 --> 00:14:07.189 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Look.

00:14:08.826 --> 00:14:11.398 position:30% line:89% align:start
(sheep baaing)

00:14:16.372 --> 00:14:19.377 position:24% line:89% align:start
(doors scrape open)

00:14:21.748 --> 00:14:24.286 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:14:35.840 --> 00:14:37.843 position:24% line:89% align:start
- Where is Mattis?

00:14:37.876 --> 00:14:39.178 position:33% line:89% align:start
- Who knows.

00:14:39.211 --> 00:14:41.582 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:14:41.617 --> 00:14:45.724 position:10% line:83% align:start
But somehow, I doubt he wants
to show his face to Ronja.

00:14:47.660 --> 00:14:49.797 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:15:11.467 --> 00:15:13.872 position:30% line:89% align:start
(crow crowing)

00:15:27.428 --> 00:15:29.765 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:15:31.869 --> 00:15:34.674 position:30% line:89% align:start
(crow crowing)

00:15:36.010 --> 00:15:38.280 position:38% line:89% align:start
(scoffs)

00:15:52.537 --> 00:15:55.309 position:21% line:83% align:start
- And where's Mattis,
the child robber?

00:15:55.342 --> 00:15:58.280 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hiding under a rock somewhere?

00:15:58.314 --> 00:16:02.287 position:27% line:83% align:start
No doubt he's too
ashamed to show his face.

00:16:02.321 --> 00:16:04.258 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

00:16:06.629 --> 00:16:08.732 position:38% line:89% align:start
(scoffs)

00:16:11.771 --> 00:16:13.875 position:38% line:89% align:start
(scoffs)

00:16:19.117 --> 00:16:21.989 position:30% line:89% align:start
(crows crowing)

00:16:24.059 --> 00:16:25.294 position:41% line:89% align:start
- Home.

00:16:26.096 --> 00:16:28.633 position:35% line:89% align:start
(footsteps)

00:16:39.719 --> 00:16:41.722 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:16:52.141 --> 00:16:54.010 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:16:54.044 --> 00:16:55.046 position:21% line:89% align:start
- What are you doing?

00:16:55.079 --> 00:16:56.582 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunting)

00:16:56.615 --> 00:16:58.785 position:13% line:89% align:start
- I won't leave my sister.

00:16:58.818 --> 00:17:01.924 position:24% line:83% align:start
I owe her too much,
she saved my life.

00:17:03.060 --> 00:17:05.396 position:10% line:89% align:start
- Sister who saved your life?

00:17:11.140 --> 00:17:17.618 position:13% line:83% align:start
- Just as Birk, my brother,
saved me many, many times over.

00:17:17.651 --> 00:17:19.554 position:30% line:89% align:start
- Your brother?

00:17:19.587 --> 00:17:21.157 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:17:21.191 --> 00:17:24.796 position:19% line:83% align:start
My enemy's child thinks
you're her brother?!

00:17:27.067 --> 00:17:30.039 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Listen to me,
she is my sister.

00:17:37.953 --> 00:17:39.088 position:30% line:89% align:start
- Your sister?!

00:17:40.189 --> 00:17:44.130 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh yes, but that's
how it all starts,

00:17:44.163 --> 00:17:46.100 position:27% line:83% align:start
and then the next
thing you know...

